Given https://www.saucedemo.com/
When user logs in with correct username and correct password
Verify user was redirected to productPage
Then user clicks 'add to cart button' of the first item Sauce Labs Backpack
Verify 'Remove' button is appears
Verify index on cart button is 1
Then user clicks on cart button
Verify user was redirected to cartPage
Verify user sees item Sauce Labs Backpack in cart
Verify checkout button is displayed
Then user clicks 'Checkout' button
Verify user was redirected to InformationPage
Then user clicks 'Continue' button
Verify user sees error message 'Error: First Name is required'
Then user enters first name, last name, zip code
Then user clicks 'Continue' button
Verify user was redirected to OverviewPage
Verify user sees total price
Then user clicks Finish button
Verify user was redirected to CompletePage
Verify user sees message "Thank you for your order!"
Verify 'Back Home' button is displayed
Then user clicks 'Back Home' button
Verify user was redirected to ProductPage


